text: Robert Walker Heathcote was an archer from Great Britain. He was born on 7 April 1847 and died on 8 April 1918. Heathcote competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Robert HeathcoteRobert HEATHCOTE == References == Category:1847 births Category:1918 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
